<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18213097-the-blood-telegram"><img alt="The Blood Telegram: Nixon, Kissinger, and a Forgotten Genocide" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1374106383l/18213097._SX98_.jpg" />
